Let E be the midpoint of \overline{AC}, then applying the Pythagorean Theorem yields
|AD|^2-|AE|^2=|DE|^2,|BD|^2-|BE|^2=|DE|^2
Therefore,
(|AD|-|BD|)(|AD|+|BD|)=189
